;The Loony Bin
NUMBER 1900
NAME The Loony Bin
REGION 1
INDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT
CHANNEL 777
CAFE
MOVEMENT_ASTRAL

CALL 49

EXIT O 1919
EXIT U 1908

ITEM 0 612
ITEM 1 1305 ADJ1=298
ITEM 2 1304 ADJ1=63
ITEM 3 85 ADJ1=345
ITEM 4 201 ADJ1=579 ADJ2=216
ITEM 5 460 ADJ1=162
PUT 5 1062 ADJ1=162 VAL2=100
ITEM 6 903 VAL1=0
ITEM 7 861 ADJ1=703

*DESCRIPTION_START
You are in the Cafe Staff Lounge, a refuge for the overworked and underpaid
Hosts and Hostesses of the Virtual Cafe. It comes complete with all of the
luxuries and necessities of home; padded walls, a very soft sofa and couch,
a Queen-sized water bed, and a hot tub. You also notice Alyssa's desk over
in the corner, on which sits a monitor that allows a view of several of the
rooms of the Virtual Cafe and other worlds.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 1
The soft couch looks extremely comfortable and inviting. Why don't you sit
down and relax a while?
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 2
The comfortable sofa looks almost as inviting as the couch. You know that if
you dare sit down, chances are you'll never get up again.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 3
This king-sized bed looks a little out of place in the Staff Lounge, but you
are glad it's here all the same! You find yourself wanting to curl up on the
bed and take a nap.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 4
This is Alyssa's personal desk. You notice schedules and very important
documents concerning the Virtual Cafe lying out for anyone to see.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 5
Hundreds of little bubbles form on the water's surface, as clouds of steam
rise from the porcelain tub. You notice that it's easily large enough for a
few dozen people to lean back and take a nice, long soak.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 7
You're not sure WHAT the damn cord does. Why don't you try pulling it?
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFPREVERB SIT -1
   CLEARVERB
   IFVAR POSITION = 1
      ECHO PLAYER You're already sitting.
   ENDIF
   IFVAR POSITION ! 1
      RANDOM DUMMY1 1 2 0
      IFVAR DUMMY1 = 1
         ECHO PLAYER You take a seat and relax on the comfortable sofa.
         ECHO OTHERS %N takes a seat and relaxes on the comfortable sofa.
      ELSE
         ECHO PLAYER You sink deeply into the cushions of the soft couch.
         ECHO OTHERS %N sinks deeply into the cushions of the soft couch.
      ENDIF
      POSITION SIT
   ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB LAY -1
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER You climb into the water bed and lie down, allowing the motion of the waves
   ECHO PLAYER to gently rock you to sleep.
   ECHO OTHERS %N climbs into the water bed for a short nap.
   POSITION LAY
   EQUAL FLAG2 1
ENDIF

IFPREVERB GO 3
   ECHO PLAYER You climb into the water bed and lie down, allowing the motion of the waves
   ECHO PLAYER to gently rock you to sleep.
   ECHO OTHERS %N climbs into the water bed for a short nap.
   CLEARVERB
   POSITION LAY
   EQUAL FLAG2 1
ENDIF

IFPREVERB POKE 3
   ECHO PLAYER Now you've done it! You poked a hole in the water bed! Sheesh, how could
   ECHO PLAYER you be so careless?!
   ECHO OTHERS That weenie %n just poked a hole in the water bed! Sheesh!
   CLEARVERB
ENDIF

IFPREVERB SEARCH 4
   ECHO PLAYER You search through Alyssa's desk, only to find a few empty tubes of lip-
   ECHO PLAYER stick, a book titled "Taming of the Shrew", and a "Kiss Me, I'm SASSY!" pin.
   ECHO OTHERS You notice %N rummaging through Alyssa's desk.
   CLEARVERB
ENDIF

IFPREVERB GO 5
   ECHO PLAYER You slowly lower yourself into the steamy hot tub, feeling the bubbles work
   ECHO PLAYER on your sore muscles, helping you to relax. You soon realize that you will
   ECHO PLAYER never get any work done again.
   ECHO OTHERS A glazed look comes over %N's face as %s lowers %iself into the steamy hot tub. You might as well give up on getting anymore work out of %i today.
   CLEARVERB
   POSITION LAY
   EQUAL FLAG2 2
ENDIF

IFPREVERB PUSH 6
   IFVAR INTNUM3 = 1
      CLEARVERB
      IFVAR ITEMVAL1 = 1
         ECHO PLAYER Host Initializing is already Active.
      ELSE
         ECHO ALL A voice from nowhere intones, "Host Initializing is now Active"
         EQUAL ITEMVAL1 1
      ENDIF
   ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB PULL 6
   IFVAR INTNUM3 = 1
      CLEARVERB
      IFVAR ITEMVAL1 = 0
         ECHO PLAYER Host Initializing is not Active.
      ELSE
         ECHO ALL A voice from nowhere intones, "Host Initializing is now Inactive"
         EQUAL ITEMVAL1 0
      ENDIF
   ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB LOOK 6
   CLEARVERB
   IFVAR INTNUM3 ! 1
      IFVAR ITEMVAL1 = 1
         ECHO PLAYER You read on the monitor, "Scripts will now recognize you as a Cafe Host."
         ECHO OTHERS %N seems changed.
         EQUAL INTNUM3 1
      ENDIF
      IFVAR ITEMVAL1 ! 1
         ECHO PLAYER You stare into the monitor and you're surprised to see Orson Wells staring
         ECHO PLAYER back at you!
         ECHO OTHERS %N stares into the monitor, but seems disappointed by what %s sees.
      ENDIF
   ELSE
      ECHO PLAYER It is used to "initiate" Hosts. PUSH activates while PULL de-activates.
   ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB TOUCH 6
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER You press your hand against the surface of the monitor.
   ECHO OTHERS %N presses %h hand against the surface of the monitor.
   IFVAR ITEMVAL2 ! 0
      EQUAL INTNUM10 ITEMVAL2
      EQUAL ITEMVAL2 0
      PLREVENT 2
      CONTPLREVENT
      ECHO PLAYER You feel a warm tingling sensation in your hand and a voice from nowhere intones, "Apartment Registration Complete."
      ECHO OTHERS A voice from nowhere intones, "Apartment Registration Complete."
   ELSE
      PLREVENT 2
      CONTPLREVENT
      ECHO ALL Nothing happens.
   ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB PULL 7
   ECHO PLAYER You pull the damn cord, and suddenly the floor opens up beneath your feet!
   ECHO OTHERS %N pulls the damn cord, and suddenly the floor opens up beneath %h feet and swallows %i!
   ECHO PLAYER You fall through the trapdoor and land in the middle of the Casino with a
   ECHO PLAYER very loud SPLAT!
   MOVE 1919
   AFFECT 1919
   ECHO OTHERS %N falls from a hole in the ceiling and lands with a very loud SPLAT!
   AFFECT 1900
   CLEARVERB
   POSITION LAY
ENDIF

IFPREVERB STAND -1
   IFVAR FLAG2 = 1
      ECHO PLAYER You slowly roll yourself out of the water bed, leaving behind the tranquil
      ECHO PLAYER waves with a small sigh.
      ECHO OTHERS %n slowly rolls %iself out of bed.
      CLEARVERB
      POSITION STAND
      EQUAL FLAG2 0
   ENDIF
   IFVAR FLAG2 = 2
      ECHO PLAYER You stand up out of the hot, bubbling water and begin to dry yourself off.
      ECHO OTHERS %n stands gets out of the hot tub, soaking wet, and begins to dry %iself off.
      CLEARVERB
      POSITION STAND
      EQUAL FLAG2 0
   ENDIF
   IFVAR FLAG2 = 3
      ECHO PLAYER You pick yourself up off the floor and dust yourself off.
      ECHO OTHERS %n picks %iself up off the floor and dusts %iself off.
      CLEARVERB
      POSITION STAND
      EQUAL FLAG2 0
   ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB WAVE -1
   IFVAR FLAG2 = 1
      ECHO PLAYER You create a mini-tidal wave on the water bed which lifts you up and tosses
      ECHO PLAYER you on to the floor!
      ECHO OTHERS %N bounces around on the water bed, causing a tidal which lifts %i up and tosses %i on to the floor!
      CLEARVERB
      POSITION LAY
      EQUAL FLAG2 3
   ENDIF
   IFVAR FLAG2 = 2
      ECHO PLAYER You wave your fingers across the surface of bubbling water.
      CLEARVERB
   ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB SLAP -1
   IFVAR FLAG2 = 2
      IFVAR PLRSINROOM < 2
         ECHO PLAYER You slap your hand on the surface of the water, splashing water everywhere!
         CLEARVERB
      ENDIF
      IFVAR PLRSINROOM => 2
         ECHO PLAYER You splash water at everyone!
         ECHO OTHERS %n splashes water at you!
         CLEARVERB
      ENDIF
   ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB JUMP -1
   ECHO PLAYER You bounce off the walls, working out your frustrations!
   ECHO OTHERS You see %N bouncing off the walls in a frenzy!
   CLEARVERB
ENDIF
