ITEM 0 204

*DESCRIPTION_START
Being a new patron, you may be a little confused about how to get started here
in the Cafe. A good way to start is to type HELP. That will give you a short
synopsis of how some of the things in the Virtual Cafe work. Also a sign is in
this room. Type the command READ SIGN to see a list of some helpful commands.
If you need further assistance, type ASSIST to get the attention of a Host.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM READ 0
The sign contains the following helpful information...

- To see what items you are carrying, type INVENTORY
- To wear an item in your inventory, type WEAR [item name]
- To see how much money you have, type WEALTH
- To see who is in the Cafe, including a Host, type WHO
- To see the description of the room again, type LOOK
- To move around in the Virtual Cafe, type N, S, E, W, etc
- To go through a door, type GO DOOR
- Once you are finished in this room, type OUT
- If you need the help of a Host, type ASSIST
- To say something, place a quote in front of what you wish to say.
  Example: "Hello.

Two helpful files to download from the Cafe Library are CAFE.MAP and VERBS.

*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 0
The sign contains the following helpful information...

- To see what items you are carrying, type INVENTORY
- To wear an item in your inventory, type WEAR [item name]
- To see how much money you have, type WEALTH
- To see who is in the Cafe, including a Host, type WHO
- To see the description of the room again, type LOOK
- To move around in the Virtual Cafe, type N, S, E, W, etc
- To go through a door, type GO DOOR
- Once you are finished in this room, type OUT
- If you need the help of a Host, type ASSIST
- To say something, place a quote in front of what you wish to say.
  Example: "Hello.

Two helpful files to download from the Cafe Library are CAFE.MAP and VERBS.

*DESCRIPTION_END
