*DESCRIPTION_START
Polished to a high gloss, the dark veined white marble floor gleams in the
dazzling light cast by an enormous crystal chandelier. An elegantly carved oak
table sits atop a richly detailed dark blue Persian rug while in the center of
the room an oval fountain, surrounded by dark pink flowered shrubs, bubbles
with ribbons of dancing water. A glowing circular portal is recessed in one of
the wall and large double plated glass doors lead out of the building.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 1
There is a picture of a bare breasted mermaid etched into the glass.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 2
This beautifully handcrafted table has a deep golden shine from the layers of
oil carefully rubbed into its dark oak pores. A sterling silver tray has been
placed on top of the buffet filled with assorted candy.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 3
It is a finely made silver tray with a lovely ivy pattern.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 4
Within the oval confines of the fountain pool, with its many spouts of
twirling water, swim a group of contented gold fish. Their eyes bulge out of
their heads like little globes. Apparently this is not an efficient design as
they seem to swim in circles a lot running into each other.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM IN 4
You see some gold fish.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 5
The gold fish swim lazily around in circles inside the fountain, occcasionally
running into each other.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFTOUCH 5
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER They avoid you.
ENDIF

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 6
Intricately woven threads create a richly colored floral pattern that seem
to pull you toward the center of the rug.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 7
Brilliant petals of light gleam from each exquisitely cut crystal shard,
casting a dazzling luminosity throughout the room.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 8
Directly above the glowing circular portal are the words "Jump Zone 1-A".
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFPREVERB D -1
   CLEARVERB
   IFVAR GEN = 0
      DISBAND
      ECHO PLAYER You head toward the restrooms and take the door marked "Men".
      MOVE 1933
      ECHO OTHERS %N goes down.
      AFFECT 1933
      ECHO OTHERS %N arrives.
   ENDIF
   IFVAR GEN = 1
      DISBAND
      ECHO PLAYER You head toward the restrooms and take the door marked "Women".
      MOVE 1930
      ECHO OTHERS %N goes down.
      AFFECT 1930
      ECHO OTHERS %N arrives.
   ENDIF
   IFVAR GEN ! 0
      IFVAR GEN ! 1
         ECHO PLAYER You try to go down, but an unseen force holds you back.
      ENDIF
   ENDIF
ENDIF

IFTOUCH 7
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER The chandelier is out of reach.
ENDIF

IFPREVERB GET -1
   IFVAR ARCHNUM = 1319
      RANDOM DUMMY1 1 4 0
      IFVAR DUMMY1 = 1
         NEWPUT 3 1319 ADJ1=152 VAL5=9
      ENDIF
      IFVAR DUMMY1 = 2
         NEWPUT 3 1319 ADJ1=347 VAL5=9
      ENDIF
      IFVAR DUMMY1 = 3
         NEWPUT 3 1319 ADJ1=54 VAL5=9
      ENDIF
      IFVAR DUMMY1 = 4
         NEWPUT 3 1319 ADJ1=259 VAL5=9
      ENDIF
   ENDIF
ENDIF

IFVERB TOUCH -1
   IFVAR ARCHNUM = 198
      IFVAR ITEMADJ1 = 77
         CLEARVERB
         ECHO PLAYER The cool water bubbles caressingly over your hand.
         ECHO OTHERS %N reaches into the fountain, letting the water stream over %h hand.
      ENDIF
   ENDIF
ENDIF
