*DESCRIPTION_START
Colorful bouquets of freshly cut flowers displayed in tall porcelain vases
brighten this marble columned lobby. Large overstuffed couches, upholstered in
muted tapestries of dark blue, deep rose and black, have been placed together
with ornately carved oak coffee tables to form several small seating groups. A
black marble counter occupies an entire wall of the lobby while polished steps
lead down to the main casino. Across from some large double oak doors, an arch
leads to the hotel's indoor swimming pool. An elevator provides easy access to
the many floors above.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 0
Each of the three large overstuffed couches look extremely comfortable and
provide a lovely place to sit while enjoying a pleasant conversation.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFPREVERB POKE 0
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER Your fingers sink deep into the thick padding of the comfortable couch.
   ECHO OTHERS %N pokes %h fingers into one of the comfortable couches.
ENDIF

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 2
Dark grey veins run through the highly reflective black marble of the long
chest-high counter, an unattended computer monitor resting on top. An elderly
clerk sits behind the counter, sleeping in his comfortable chair.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 3
Tall frilly gladiolas, bright yellow daffodils, dark pink chrysanthemums and
stark white freesias are artfully arranged in the tall vases.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 5
Through the arch you can see the hotel swimming pool.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFPREVERB EXAM 6
   CLEARVERB
   IFVAR AZHFLOORNUM ! RNUM
      ECHO PLAYER The elevator is closed. You notice a glowing button on the wall beside it.
   ELSE
      ECHO PLAYER The elevator is open.
   ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB GO 6
   CLEARVERB
   IFVAR AZHFLOORNUM ! RNUM
      ECHO PLAYER The elevator is closed. You notice a glowing button on the wall beside it.
