;
;Honeymoon Suite
;NUMBER 1908
;REGION 1
;NAME Hotel Escapades, Honeymoon Suite
;INDOOR_FLOOR
;FIXED_LIGHT
;CAFE
;MOVEMENT_ASTRAL
;CHANNEL 777
;
;CALL 49
;
;
;Hotel Elevator
NUMBER 1909
REGION 1
NAME Hotel Escapades, Elevator
INDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT
CAFE
MOVEMENT_ASTRAL
CHANNEL 777

CALL 49

RELOGIN 1903
EXIT O 1909

ITEM 0 282 ADJ1=292
ITEM 1 247 ADJ1=145
EXTEND 1 labeled 1
ITEM 2 247 ADJ1=145
EXTEND 2 labeled 2
ITEM 3 247 ADJ1=145
EXTEND 3 labeled 3
ITEM 4 247 ADJ1=145
EXTEND 4 labeled 4
ITEM 5 247 ADJ1=145
EXTEND 5 labeled 5
ITEM 6 802

*DESCRIPTION_START
The elegance of the hotel is carried over into this spacious elevator, soothing
music playing in the background and soft plush red carpeting underfoot. Several
glowing numbered buttons, obviously corresponding to the various floors of the
hotel, adorn a brass panel beside the elevator doors.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFPREVERB EXAM 0
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER The panel contains five glowing buttons...%c
   ECHO PLAYER Button 1 - 1st Floor (Hotel Lobby)
   ECHO PLAYER Button 2 - 2nd Floor
   ECHO PLAYER Button 3 - 3rd Floor
   ECHO PLAYER Button 4 - 4th Floor
   ECHO PLAYER Button 5 - 5th Floor%c
   IFVAR AZHFLOORNUM = 0
      ECHO PLAYER A digital display shows that you are between floors.
   ENDIF
   IFVAR AZHFLOORNUM = 1903
      ECHO PLAYER A digital display shows that you are on the 1st floor - the Hotel Lobby.
   ENDIF
   IFVAR AZHFLOORNUM = 1904
      ECHO PLAYER A digital display shows that you are on the 2nd floor.
   ENDIF
   IFVAR AZHFLOORNUM = 1905
      ECHO PLAYER A digital display shows that you are on the 3rd floor.
   ENDIF
   IFVAR AZHFLOORNUM = 1906
      ECHO PLAYER A digital display shows that you are on the 4th floor.
   ENDIF
   IFVAR AZHFLOORNUM = 1907
      ECHO PLAYER A digital display shows that you are on the 5th floor.
   ENDIF
   IFVAR AZHFLOORNUM = 1908
      ECHO PLAYER A digital display shows that you are on the 6th floor - the Honeymoon Suite.
   ENDIF
   ECHO PLAYER %cYou also notice a small card slot below the glowing buttons.
ENDIF

IFPREVERB O -1
   CLEARVERB
   IFVAR POSITION > 0
      ECHO PLAYER You'll have to stand up first.
   ELSE
      IFVAR AZHFLOORNUM ! 0
         MOVEGROUP AZHFLOORNUM
         AFFECT AZHFLOORNUM
         ECHO OTHGROUP %P arrives from the elevator.
      ELSE
         ECHO PLAYER The elevator doors are closed.
      ENDIF
   ENDIF
ENDIF

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 1
It is labeled 1.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFVERB PUSH 1
   IFVAR AZHFLOORNUM = 1903
      ECHO PLAYER You notice that you're already on the first floor.
   ELSE
      EQUAL AZHELEBUT1 1
   ENDIF
ENDIF

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 2
It is labeled 2.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFVERB PUSH 2
   IFVAR AZHFLOORNUM = 1904
      ECHO PLAYER You notice that you're already on the 2nd floor.
   ELSE
      EQUAL AZHELEBUT2 1
   ENDIF
ENDIF

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 3
It is labeled 3.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFVERB PUSH 3
   IFVAR AZHFLOORNUM = 1905
      ECHO PLAYER You notice that you're already on the 3rd floor.
   ELSE
      EQUAL AZHELEBUT3 1
   ENDIF
ENDIF

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 4
It is labeled 4.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFVERB PUSH 4
   IFVAR AZHFLOORNUM = 1906
      ECHO PLAYER You notice that you're already on the 4th floor.
   ELSE
      EQUAL AZHELEBUT4 1
   ENDIF
ENDIF

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 5
It is labeled 5.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFVERB PUSH 5
   IFVAR AZHFLOORNUM = 1907
      ECHO PLAYER You notice that you're already on the 5th floor.
   ELSE
      EQUAL AZHELEBUT5 1
   ENDIF
ENDIF
