;Casino Central
NUMBER 1919
REGION 1
NAME Casino Central
INDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT
CAFE
MOVEMENT_ASTRAL
CHANNEL 777

CALL 49

EXIT U 1903
EXIT N 1919
EXIT S 1920
EXIT E 1925
EXIT W 1924
EXIT SE 1926

ITEM 0 532
ITEM 1 853 ADJ1=1372
ITEM 2 529
ITEM 3 204 ADJ1=178
EXTEND 3 ringed with flashing lights
ITEM 4 1249 ADJ1=77
ITEM 5 1594

*DESCRIPTION_START
Dangling from the high beamed ceiling of this enormous casino is an immense
crystal chandelier, with heavily laden arms of prisms, each casting a brilliant
little rainbow on the shiny chrome slot machines below. Deeply padded crimson
carpet helps to muffle the clanking of the one-armed bandits and the clatter of
change falling into their trays. Bits of heated conversations drift in from the
various surrounding rooms, adding to the already excited tension pervading the
casino. Polished steps lead to the Hotel Escapades above.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 0
Protruding from the side of the slot machine its chrome arm. Go ahead. Give
it a pull.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFPREVERB PULL 0
   CLEARVERB
   IFVAR WEALTH1 < 1
      ECHO PLAYER You don't have enough money to play the slots.
   ENDIF
   IFVAR WEALTH1 => 1
      IFVAR ROUNDTIME > 0
         STRCVT 0 ROUNDTIME
         ECHO PLAYER [Wait %0 seconds...]
      ENDIF
      IFVAR ROUNDTIME = 0
         EQUAL ROUNDTIME 5
         ECHO PLAYER You plug a dollar into the slot..."kachink" and pull the arm. You see:
         ROUTINE 4
         RANDOM DUMMY1 1 10 0
         IFVAR DUMMY1 = 1
            ECHO OTHERS You notice %n playing the slot machines.
         ENDIF
      ENDIF
   ENDIF
ENDIF

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 1
They don't call them "one-armed bandits" for nothing. The slot machine seems
to practically leer at you with a chrome plated grimace to pull its arm.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFPREVERB KICK 1
   RANDOM DUMMY1 1 20 0
   IFVAR DUMMY1 > 9
      IFVAR DUMMY1 > 12
         CLEARVERB
         IFVAR WEALTH1 => 5
            ECHO PLAYER You kick the slot machine, causing $5.00 worth of damage. The busboy comes by
            ECHO PLAYER to collect the money.
            ECHO OTHERS %N kicks the slot machine, causing minor damage. The busyboy comes by and collects some money from %i.
            SUB WEALTH1 5
         ELSE
            ECHO PLAYER You kick the slot machine, causing $5.00 worth of damage. Unfortunately, you
            ECHO PLAYER don't have the funds required to pay for repairs, so the busboy comes by and
            DAMAGEPLR CRUSH 5 roughs you up.
            ECHO OTHERS %N kicks the slot machine, causing $5.00 worth of damage. Unfortunately, %s doesn't have the funds required to pay for repairs, so the busyboy comes by and roughs %i up.
         ENDIF
      ELSE
         RANDOM DUMMY2 1 20 0
         IFVAR DUMMY2 > 10
            CLEARVERB
            ECHO PLAYER You kick the slot machine, and some money spills out!
            ADD WEALTH1 5
          ENDIF
      ENDIF
   ENDIF
ENDIF

IFVERB LEAN 1
   RANDOM DUMMY1 1 5 0
   IFVAR DUMMY1 = 5
      ECHO ALL The slot machine wobbles under the added weight.
   ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB FUCK 1
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER You attempt to mate with the slot machine but find your parts incompatible.
   ECHO OTHERS %N unsuccssfully attempts to mate with a slot machine.
ENDIF

IFPREVERB KISS 1
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER You plant a big sloppy kiss on the front of the slot machine.
   ECHO OTHERS %N plants a big sloppy kiss on the front of the slot machine.
ENDIF

IFPREVERB CUDDLE 1
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER You cuddle up to a slot machine in hope that your luck will improve.
   ECHO OTHERS %N tries to bribe a slot machine with sexual favors.
ENDIF

IFPREVERB NUZZLE 1
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER You nuzzle the cold slot machine with your nose.
   ECHO OTHERS %N tries to get friendly with a slot machine.
ENDIF

IFPREVERB HIT 1
   RANDOM DUMMY1 1 5 0
   IFVAR DUMMY1 > 3
      CLEARVERB
      ECHO PLAYER You strike the slot machine, causing no damage to it, and hurting your fist
      ECHO PLAYER in the process.
      ECHO OTHERS %N strikes the slot machine, causing no damage to it, and hurting %h fist in the process.
   ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB THUMP 1
   RANDOM DUMMY1 1 5 0
   IFVAR DUMMY1 > 3
      CLEARVERB
      ECHO PLAYER You strike the slot machine, causing no damage to it, and hurting your fist
      ECHO PLAYER in the process.
      ECHO OTHERS %N strikes the slot machine, causing no damage to it, and hurting %h fist in the process.
   ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB IGNITE 1
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER You attempt to set fire to a slot machine, but a busboy comes by and thumps
   ECHO PLAYER you on the head with a fire extinguisher.
   ECHO OTHERS %N attempts to set fire to a slot machine, but a busy boy comes by and thumps %i on the head with a fire extinguisher.
ENDIF

IFPREVERB LICK 1
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER You drool all over a slot machine.
   ECHO OTHERS %N drools all over a slot machine.
ENDIF

IFPREVERB SHOVE 1
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER You shove against a slot machine.
   ECHO OTHERS %N shoves against a slot machine.
ENDIF

IFPREVERB GLARE 1
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER You glare at a slot machine.
   ECHO OTHERS %N gives a slot machine a dirty look.
ENDIF

IFPREVERB ROAR 1
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER You roar at a slot machine.
   ECHO OTHERS %N roars at a slot machine.
ENDIF

IFPREVERB CLIMB 2
   CLEARVERB
   IFVAR FLAG1 ! 0
      ECHO PLAYER You're already on the stool.
   ELSE
      ECHO PLAYER You clamber up to stand on top of a stool.
      ECHO OTHERS %N clambers up to stand on top of a stool.
      EQUAL FLAG1 2
   ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB TURN 2
   IFVAR FLAG1 > 1
      CLEARVERB
      ECHO PLAYER You adjust your stance on the stool, preparing to jump down.
      ECHO OTHERS %N positions %iself for a jump.
      EQUAL FLAG1 3
   ENDIF
   IFVAR FLAG1 < 2
      IFVAR POSITION = 1
         CLEARVERB
         ECHO PLAYER You spin around on your stool.
         ECHO OTHERS %N spins around on %h stool.
      ENDIF
      IFVAR POSITION ! 1
         CLEARVERB
         ECHO PLAYER You give a stool a spin.
         ECHO OTHERS %N gives a stool a spin.
      ENDIF
   ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB READ 3
   CLEARVERB
   IFVAR PVAL39 > 0
      STRCVT 0 PVAL39
      ECHO PLAYER CURRENT SLOT MACHINE JACKPOT: $%0.00!
   ENDIF
   IFVAR PVAL39 < 1
      ECHO PLAYER Egads! The current jackpot is zero!
   ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB EXAM 3
   CLEARVERB
   IFVAR PVAL39 > 0
      STRCVT 0 PVAL39
      ECHO PLAYER CURRENT SLOT MACHINE JACKPOT: $%0.00!
   ENDIF
   IFVAR PVAL39 < 1
      ECHO PLAYER Egads! The current jackpot is zero!
   ENDIF
ENDIF

IFTOUCH 4
   CLEARVERB
   IFVAR FLAG1 > 1
      EQUAL ROUNDTIME 6
      ECHO PLAYER You jump from the stool and grab onto the crystal chandelier, swinging back
      ECHO PLAYER and forth above the casino.
      ECHO OTHERS %N jumps from the stool and grabs onto the crystal chandelier, swinging back and forth above the casino.
      RANDOM DUMMY1 1 10 0
      IFVAR DUMMY1 > 5
         PLREVENT 2
         CONTPLREVENT
         POSITION LAY
         DAMAGEPLR CRUSH 5 Unable to hold on any longer, you lose your grip and fall to the floor below.
         ECHO OTHERS Unable to hold on any longer, %N loses %h grip and falls to the floor below.
         EQUAL FLAG1 1
      ENDIF
      IFVAR DUMMY1 < 6
         POSITION STAND
         PLREVENT 2
         CONTPLREVENT
         ECHO PLAYER You let go of the chandelier, do a flip in mid-air, and land on your feet!
         ECHO OTHERS %N lets go of the chandelier, does a flip in mid-air, and lands on %h feet!
         EQUAL FLAG1 0
      ENDIF
   ELSE
      ECHO PLAYER You can't reach that from here.
   ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB JUMP -1
   IFVAR FLAG1 = 2
      CLEARVERB
      ECHO PLAYER You hop down off the stool.
      ECHO OTHERS %N hops down off a stool.
      EQUAL FLAG1 0
      POSITION STAND
   ENDIF
   IFVAR FLAG1 = 3
      CLEARVERB
      RANDOM DUMMY1 1 10 0
      IFVAR DUMMY1 > 5
         ECHO PLAYER You leap into the air from the stool, do a flip in the air and land on your fanny.
         ECHO OTHERS %N leaps into the air from the top of a stool, does a forward flip and lands on %h fanny.
         POSITION SIT
         EQUAL FLAG1 1
      ELSE
         ECHO PLAYER You leap into the air from the stool, do a flip in the air and land on your feet!
         ECHO OTHERS %N leaps into the air from the top of a stool, does a forward flip and lands on %h feet!
         POSITION STAND
         EQUAL FLAG1 0
      ENDIF
   ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB SIT -1
   CLEARVERB
   IFVAR POSITION = 1
      ECHO PLAYER You make yourself more comfortable on your stool.
   ENDIF
   IFVAR POSITION ! 1
      ECHO PLAYER You take a seat on a stool.
      ECHO OTHERS %N sits on a stool.
   ENDIF
   EQUAL FLAG1 0
   POSITION SIT
ENDIF

IFPREVERB STAND -1
   IFVAR FLAG1 = 0
      IFVAR POSITION ! 0
         CLEARVERB
         ECHO PLAYER You slide onto your feet.
         ECHO OTHERS %N slides onto %h feet.
         POSITION STAND
      ENDIF
   ENDIF
   IFVAR FLAG1 = 1
      CLEARVERB
      ECHO PLAYER You stand up and dust yourself off.
      ECHO OTHERS %N stands up and dusts %iself off.
      EQUAL FLAG1 0
      POSITION STAND
   ENDIF
   IFVAR FLAG1 > 1
      CLEARVERB
      ECHO PLAYER You're standing on top of the stool.
   ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB LAY -1
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER Feeling faint from all the excitement?
   ECHO OTHERS %N looks like %s might pass out.
ENDIF

IFPREVERB NORTH -1
   CLEARVERB
   IFVAR GEN = 0
      DISBAND
      ECHO PLAYER You head toward the restrooms and take the door marked "Men".
      MOVE 1933
      ECHO OTHERS %N goes north.
      AFFECT 1933
      ECHO OTHERS %N arrives.
   ENDIF
   IFVAR GEN = 1
      DISBAND
      ECHO PLAYER You head toward the restrooms and take the door marked "Women".
      MOVE 1930
      ECHO OTHERS %N goes north.
      AFFECT 1930
      ECHO OTHERS %N arrives.
   ENDIF
   IFVAR GEN ! 0
      IFVAR GEN ! 1
         ECHO PLAYER You try to go north, but an unseen force holds you back.
      ENDIF
   ENDIF
ENDIF

IFVERB SEARCH -1
   ECHO PLAYER You search around for a good machine and find one with a spare stool too.
ENDIF

IFPREVERB HIDE -1
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER As you grope around trying to hide, you notice several security cameras
   ECHO PLAYER panning the casino and a busboy keeping a close eye on you.
   ECHO OTHERS %N suddenly looks very paranoid.
ENDIF

IFENTRY
   IFVAR PVAL39 > 0
      STRCVT 0 PVAL39
      ECHO GROUP As you enter you notice a lighted sign above the slot machines, flashing: %cCURRENT SLOT MACHINE JACKPOT: $%0.00!
   ENDIF
ENDIF
