*DESCRIPTION_START
The walls of the Holodeck are a gold on black gridwork, matching the ceiling
and floor in a soft, shadowy radiance. A single chrome pedestal stands at the
center of the room. A door, recessed in one of the smooth walls, leads back
out into the lobby.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 1
The pedestal is engraved.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM READ 1
The following programs are available for your enjoyment:

          Ancient Castle       Rushing River
          Arabian Nights       Western Saloon
          Backseat             Secluded Grove
          Barn Loft            Snowy Deck
          Cabin Hideaway       Undersea
          Fern Grotto          Waterfall
          Island Beach

Instructions:

 1. To run a program, say RUN PROGRAM followed by the program name
 2. To end a program, say END PROGRAM
 3. To leave a continuing program, say LEAVE PROGRAM
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFSAY OPEN_DOOR
   IFITEM 2 OPEN
      ECHO ALL A soft voice from nowhere says, "The door is already open."
   ENDIF
   IFITEM 2 CLOSED
      OPEN 2
      ECHO ALL The door slides open.
      AFFECT 1920
      OPEN 1
      ECHO ALL The door to Holodeck 1 slides open.
   ENDIF
ENDIF

