The following programs are available for your enjoyment:

          Ancient Castle       Rushing River
          Arabian Nights       Western Saloon
          Backseat             Secluded Grove
          Barn Loft            Snowy Deck
          Cabin Hideaway       Undersea
          Fern Grotto          Waterfall
          Island Beach

Instructions:

 1. To run a program, say RUN PROGRAM followed by the program name
 2. To end a program, say END PROGRAM
 3. To leave a continuing program, say LEAVE PROGRAM
*DESCRIPTION_END

