;
;
;HIGH FIVE
NUMBER 1924
NAME The High Five Table
REGION 1
INDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT
CAFE
MOVEMENT_ASTRAL
CHANNEL 777

CALL 49

EXIT O 1919

ITEM 0 396 ADJ1=961 ADJ2=1314
ITEM 1 586
ITEM 2 529 ADJ1=259 ADJ2=180
ITEM 3 1249 ADJ1=663
EXTEND 3 draped with ropes of dazzling crystals
ITEM 4 345 ADJ1=482
ITEM 5 67 ADJ1=961 ADJ2=1314
ITEM 6 204

*DESCRIPTION_START
A magnificent chandelier, draped with ropes of dazzling crystals, hangs above
an elongated curved rectangular table. Standing waist-high, its claw feet sunk
into the deep blue variegated carpeting, the High Five table glows with a dull
sheen from the layers of oil carefully rubbed into its oak sides, the High Five
dealer standing directly behind it. Clusters of vibrant green shrubs nestle in
the corners of the room which is decorated with ornately framed oil paintings.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 0
A row of red leather stools lines the front of the table, making it convient
to rest while you do a little gambling. A young man dressed in a three-piece
suit stands behind it, a pair of dice rests on top of it and a small sign has
been attached to the front of it.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFPREVERB GO 0
   CLEARVERB
   EQUAL ROUNDTIME 10
   ECHO PLAYER You stretch out on top of the High Five table.
   ECHO OTHERS %N stretches out on top of the High Five table.
   PLREVENT 1
   ECHO PLAYER The dealer thumps you hard on the head and then shoves you off into the floor.
   ECHO OTHERS The dealer thumps %N hard on the head and then shoves %i off into the floor.
   POSITION LAY
ENDIF

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 1
They look like your average six-sided dice.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFPREVERB KISS 1
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER You blow on the dice.
   ECHO OTHERS %N blows on the dice.
   RANDOM DUMMY1 1 5 0
   IFVAR DUMMY1 ! 5
      ECHO PLAYER You feel lucky!
   ENDIF
   IFVAR DUMMY1 = 5
      ECHO PLAYER As if THAT's gonna do any good.
   ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB ROLL 1
   CLEARVERB
   IFVAR ROUNDTIME ! 0
      STRCVT 0 ROUNDTIME
      ECHO PLAYER [Wait %0 seconds...]
   ENDIF
   IFVAR ROUNDTIME = 0
      IFVAR WEALTH1 < 8
         ECHO PLAYER You must have at least $8.00 to play High Five.
      ENDIF
      IFVAR WEALTH1 > 7
         EQUAL ROUNDTIME 8
         ECHO PLAYER You place 8 bucks on the table and pick up your dice, giving them a toss.
         RANDOM FLAG1 1 10 0
         IFVAR FLAG1 = 10
            ECHO OTHERS You notice %N playing High Five.
         ENDIF

         RANDOM AZD1 1 6 0
         RANDOM AZD2 1 6 0
         RANDOM AZD3 1 6 0
         RANDOM AZD4 1 6 0
         RANDOM AZD5 1 6 0

         IFVAR AZD1 = 1
            STRCPY 0 "|.......|.
            STRCPY 1 "|...O...|.
            STRCPY 2 "|.......|.
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD1 = 2
            STRCPY 0 "|.O.....|.
            STRCPY 1 "|.......|.
            STRCPY 2 "|.....O.|.
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD1 = 3
            STRCPY 0 "|.....O.|.
            STRCPY 1 "|...O...|.
            STRCPY 2 "|.O.....|.
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD1 = 4
            STRCPY 0 "|.O...O.|.
            STRCPY 1 "|.......|.
            STRCPY 2 "|.O...O.|.
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD1 = 5
            STRCPY 0 "|.O...O.|.
            STRCPY 1 "|...O...|.
            STRCPY 2 "|.O...O.|.
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD1 = 6
            STRCPY 0 "|.O...O.|.
            STRCPY 1 "|.O...O.|.
            STRCPY 2 "|.O...O.|.
         ENDIF

         IFVAR AZD2 = 1
            STRCAT 0 "|.......|.
            STRCAT 1 "|...O...|.
            STRCAT 2 "|.......|.
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD2 = 2
            STRCAT 0 "|.O.....|.
            STRCAT 1 "|.......|.
            STRCAT 2 "|.....O.|.
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD2 = 3
            STRCAT 0 "|.....O.|.
            STRCAT 1 "|...O...|.
            STRCAT 2 "|.O.....|.
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD2 = 4
            STRCAT 0 "|.O...O.|.
            STRCAT 1 "|.......|.
            STRCAT 2 "|.O...O.|.
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD2 = 5
            STRCAT 0 "|.O...O.|.
            STRCAT 1 "|...O...|.
            STRCAT 2 "|.O...O.|.
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD2 = 6
            STRCAT 0 "|.O...O.|.
            STRCAT 1 "|.O...O.|.
            STRCAT 2 "|.O...O.|.
         ENDIF

         IFVAR AZD3 = 1
            STRCAT 0 "|.......|.
            STRCAT 1 "|...O...|.
            STRCAT 2 "|.......|.
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD3 = 2
            STRCAT 0 "|.O.....|.
            STRCAT 1 "|.......|.
            STRCAT 2 "|.....O.|.
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD3 = 3
            STRCAT 0 "|.....O.|.
            STRCAT 1 "|...O...|.
            STRCAT 2 "|.O.....|.
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD3 = 4
            STRCAT 0 "|.O...O.|.
            STRCAT 1 "|.......|.
            STRCAT 2 "|.O...O.|.
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD3 = 5
            STRCAT 0 "|.O...O.|.
            STRCAT 1 "|...O...|.
            STRCAT 2 "|.O...O.|.
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD3 = 6
            STRCAT 0 "|.O...O.|.
            STRCAT 1 "|.O...O.|.
            STRCAT 2 "|.O...O.|.
         ENDIF

         IFVAR AZD4 = 1
            STRCAT 0 "|.......|.
            STRCAT 1 "|...O...|.
            STRCAT 2 "|.......|.
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD4 = 2
            STRCAT 0 "|.O.....|.
            STRCAT 1 "|.......|.
            STRCAT 2 "|.....O.|.
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD4 = 3
            STRCAT 0 "|.....O.|.
            STRCAT 1 "|...O...|.
            STRCAT 2 "|.O.....|.
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD4 = 4
            STRCAT 0 "|.O...O.|.
            STRCAT 1 "|.......|.
            STRCAT 2 "|.O...O.|.
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD4 = 5
            STRCAT 0 "|.O...O.|.
            STRCAT 1 "|...O...|.
            STRCAT 2 "|.O...O.|.
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD4 = 6
            STRCAT 0 "|.O...O.|.
            STRCAT 1 "|.O...O.|.
            STRCAT 2 "|.O...O.|.
         ENDIF

         IFVAR AZD5 = 1
            STRCAT 0 "|.......|
            STRCAT 1 "|...O...|
            STRCAT 2 "|.......|
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD5 = 2
            STRCAT 0 "|.O.....|
            STRCAT 1 "|.......|
            STRCAT 2 "|.....O.|
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD5 = 3
            STRCAT 0 "|.....O.|
            STRCAT 1 "|...O...|
            STRCAT 2 "|.O.....|
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD5 = 4
            STRCAT 0 "|.O...O.|
            STRCAT 1 "|.......|
            STRCAT 2 "|.O...O.|
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD5 = 5
            STRCAT 0 "|.O...O.|
            STRCAT 1 "|...O...|
            STRCAT 2 "|.O...O.|
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD5 = 6
            STRCAT 0 "|.O...O.|
            STRCAT 1 "|.O...O.|
            STRCAT 2 "|.O...O.|
         ENDIF

         ECHO PLAYER %c+-------+ +-------+ +-------+ +-------+ +-------+%c%0%c%1%c%2%c+-------+ +-------+ +-------+ +-------+ +-------+

         EQUAL AZ1S 0
         EQUAL AZ2S 0
         EQUAL AZ3S 0
         EQUAL AZ4S 0
         EQUAL AZ5S 0
         EQUAL AZ6S 0
         EQUAL AZHF 0
         EQUAL AZLS 0
         EQUAL AZ4K 0
         EQUAL AZSS 0
         EQUAL AZFH 0
         EQUAL AZ3K 0
         EQUAL AZ2P 0
         EQUAL AZ1P 0
         EQUAL AZNT 1
         EQUAL AZDS 0

         IFVAR AZD1 = 1
            ADD AZ1S 1
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD1 = 2
            ADD AZ2S 1
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD1 = 3
            ADD AZ3S 1
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD1 = 4
            ADD AZ4S 1
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD1 = 5
            ADD AZ5S 1
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD1 = 6
            ADD AZ6S 1
         ENDIF

         IFVAR AZD2 = 1
            ADD AZ1S 1
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD2 = 2
            ADD AZ2S 1
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD2 = 3
            ADD AZ3S 1
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD2 = 4
            ADD AZ4S 1
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD2 = 5
            ADD AZ5S 1
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD2 = 6
            ADD AZ6S 1
         ENDIF

         IFVAR AZD3 = 1
            ADD AZ1S 1
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD3 = 2
            ADD AZ2S 1
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD3 = 3
            ADD AZ3S 1
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD3 = 4
            ADD AZ4S 1
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD3 = 5
            ADD AZ5S 1
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD3 = 6
            ADD AZ6S 1
         ENDIF

         IFVAR AZD4 = 1
            ADD AZ1S 1
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD4 = 2
            ADD AZ2S 1
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD4 = 3
            ADD AZ3S 1
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD4 = 4
            ADD AZ4S 1
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD4 = 5
            ADD AZ5S 1
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD4 = 6
            ADD AZ6S 1
         ENDIF

         IFVAR AZD5 = 1
            ADD AZ1S 1
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD5 = 2
            ADD AZ2S 1
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD5 = 3
            ADD AZ3S 1
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD5 = 4
            ADD AZ4S 1
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD5 = 5
            ADD AZ5S 1
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZD5 = 6
            ADD AZ6S 1
         ENDIF

         ADD AZDS AZD1
         ADD AZDS AZD2
         ADD AZDS AZD3
         ADD AZDS AZD4
         ADD AZDS AZD5

         IFVAR AZ1S = 5
            EQUAL AZHF 1
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZ2S = 5
            EQUAL AZHF 1
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZ3S = 5
            EQUAL AZHF 1
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZ4S = 5
            EQUAL AZHF 1
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZ5S = 5
            EQUAL AZHF 1
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZ6S = 5
            EQUAL AZHF 1
         ENDIF

         IFVAR AZ1S = 4
            EQUAL AZ4K 1
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZ2S = 4
            EQUAL AZ4K 1
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZ3S = 4
            EQUAL AZ4K 1
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZ4S = 4
            EQUAL AZ4K 1
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZ5S = 4
            EQUAL AZ4K 1
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZ6S = 4
            EQUAL AZ4K 1
         ENDIF

         IFVAR AZ1S = 1
            IFVAR AZ2S = 1
               IFVAR AZ3S = 1
                  IFVAR AZ4S = 1
                     IFVAR AZ5S = 1
                        EQUAL AZLS 1
                     ENDIF
                     IFVAR AZ5S ! 1
                        EQUAL AZSS 1
                     ENDIF
                  ENDIF
               ENDIF
            ENDIF
         ENDIF

         IFVAR AZ2S = 1
            IFVAR AZ3S = 1
               IFVAR AZ4S = 1
                  IFVAR AZ5S = 1
                     IFVAR AZ6S = 1
                        EQUAL AZLS 1
                     ENDIF
                     IFVAR AZ6S ! 1
                        EQUAL AZSS 1
                     ENDIF
                  ENDIF
               ENDIF
            ENDIF
         ENDIF

         IFVAR AZLS = 0
            IFVAR AZ3S = 1
               IFVAR AZ4S = 1
                  IFVAR AZ5S = 1
                     IFVAR AZ6S = 1
                        EQUAL AZSS 1
                     ENDIF
                  ENDIF
               ENDIF
            ENDIF
         ENDIF

         IFVAR AZ1S = 3
            EQUAL AZ3K 1
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZ2S = 3
            EQUAL AZ3K 1
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZ3S = 3
            EQUAL AZ3K 1
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZ4S = 3
            EQUAL AZ3K 1
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZ5S = 3
            EQUAL AZ3K 1
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZ6S = 3
            EQUAL AZ3K 1
         ENDIF

         IFVAR AZ1S = 2
            EQUAL AZ1P 1
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZ2S = 2
            IFVAR AZ1P ! 0
               EQUAL AZ2P 2
            ENDIF
            IFVAR AZ1P = 0
               EQUAL AZ1P 2
            ENDIF
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZ3S = 2
            IFVAR AZ1P ! 0
               EQUAL AZ2P 3
            ENDIF
            IFVAR AZ1P = 0
               EQUAL AZ1P 3
            ENDIF
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZ4S = 2
            IFVAR AZ1P ! 0
               EQUAL AZ2P 4
            ENDIF
            IFVAR AZ1P = 0
               EQUAL AZ1P 4
            ENDIF
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZ5S = 2
            IFVAR AZ1P ! 0
               EQUAL AZ2P 5
            ENDIF
            IFVAR AZ1P = 0
               EQUAL AZ1P 5
            ENDIF
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZ6S = 2
            IFVAR AZ1P ! 0
               EQUAL AZ2P 6
            ENDIF
            IFVAR AZ1P = 0
               EQUAL AZ1P 6
            ENDIF
         ENDIF

         IFVAR AZ3K = 1
            IFVAR AZ1P ! 0
               EQUAL AZFH 1
            ENDIF
         ENDIF

         IFVAR AZHF = 1
            ECHO PLAYER You rolled a High Five!
            ECHO ALL %N rolled a High Five!
            MULT AZDS 10
            EQUAL AZNT 0
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZLS = 1
            ECHO PLAYER You rolled a Large Straight!
            EQUAL AZDS 40
            EQUAL AZSS 0
            EQUAL AZNT 0
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZ4K = 1
            ECHO PLAYER You rolled Four of a Kind!
            MULT AZDS 2
            EQUAL AZNT 0
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZSS = 1
            ECHO PLAYER You rolled a Small Straight!
            EQUAL AZDS 30
            EQUAL AZNT 0
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZFH = 1
            ECHO PLAYER You rolled a Full House.
            EQUAL AZDS 25
            EQUAL AZ3K 0
            EQUAL AZ1P 0
            EQUAL AZNT 0
        ENDIF
         IFVAR AZ3K = 1
            ECHO PLAYER You rolled a Three of a Kind.
            EQUAL AZNT 0
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZ2P ! 0
            STRCVT 1 AZ1P
            STRCVT 2 AZ2P
            ECHO PLAYER You rolled a pair of %1's and %2's.
            EQUAL AZDS AZ2P
            ADD AZDS AZ1P
            EQUAL AZ1P 0
            EQUAL AZNT 0
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZ1P ! 0
            STRCVT 1 AZ1P
            ECHO PLAYER You rolled a pair of %1's.
            EQUAL AZDS AZ1P
            EQUAL AZNT 0
         ENDIF
         IFVAR AZNT = 1
            EQUAL AZDS 0
            ECHO PLAYER You rolled absolutely nothing.
         ENDIF

         IFVAR AZDS ! 0
            STRCVT 0 AZDS
            ECHO PLAYER The dealer gives you $%0.00.
            ADD WEALTH1 AZDS
         ENDIF
         SUB WEALTH1 8

      ENDIF
   ENDIF
ENDIF

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 2
It looks to be fairly comfortable.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFPREVERB GO 2
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER You hop up on one of the red leather stools.
   ECHO OTHERS %N hops up on one of the red leather stools.
   POSITION SIT
ENDIF

IFPREVERB TURN 2
   IFVAR POSITION = 1
      CLEARVERB
      ECHO PLAYER You spin around on your stool.
      ECHO OTHERS %N spins around on %h stool.
   ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB CLIMB 2
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER The dealer shakes his head at you as you attempt to climb up on the stool.
   ECHO OTHERS %N attempts to climb up on the stool, but a stern look from the dealer stops %i.
ENDIF

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 3
The chandelier hangs several feet above the table, casting a brilliant light
throughout the room.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFTOUCH 3
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER You can't reach that.
ENDIF

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 4
One of the paintings is of a silver, almost machine-like bodybuilder posing
on a circular platform suspended in a blue-green mist. You notice a signature
in the lower right corner that reads M.J. Breyette.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 5
The High Five dealer is dressed in a fashionable three-piece suit. Perhaps if
you listened to him, he'd tell you how to play the game.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFTOUCH 5
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER The dealer remains a polite distance from you.
ENDIF

IFVERB LISTEN 5
   ECHO PLAYER The dealer explains, "High Five is a game of chance played with 5 six-sided
   ECHO PLAYER dice. The object of the game is to roll the best possible combination, which is
   ECHO PLAYER five of a kind... or a High Five. Each roll costs $8, and you must wait eight
   ECHO PLAYER seconds between each roll. For a list of different dice combinations and their
   ECHO PLAYER payoff values, take a look at the sign attached to the front of the table."
ENDIF

IFPREVERB FROWN 5
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER You frown at %a.
   ECHO OTHERS %N glares at %a.
ENDIF

IFPREVERB GLARE 5
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER You glare at %a.
   ECHO OTHERS %n glares at %a.
ENDIF

IFPREVERB GROWL 5
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER You growl at %a.
   ECHO OTHERS %N growls at %a.
ENDIF

