ITEM 2 398

*DESCRIPTION_START
You are in a utilitarian bathroom stall. The usual items one would expect to be
in a room of this sort are here, such as a commode and some graffiti written on
the wall.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM READ 0
The graffiti reads, "Flush 3 times. It's a long way to th..." but ends rather
abruptly.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 0
The graffiti reads, "Flush 3 times. It's a long way to th..." but ends rather
abruptly.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 1
It looks like any other commode you've ever seen before in a public restroom.
It has a padded seat for your comfort, and a silver handle for flushing.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFPREVERB GO 1
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER All you have to do is sit.
ENDIF

IFPREVERB PULL 2
   CLEARVERB
   ADD FLAG1 1
   IFVAR FLAG1 < 3
      ECHO PLAYER The contents of the commode gurgle down the drain.
      AFFECT 1930
      ECHO OTHERS You hear the sound of a commode flushing coming from one of the stalls.
   ENDIF
   IFVAR FLAG1 > 2
      IFVAR POSITION = 1
         ECHO PLAYER Three time's the charm! The rim of the commode seems to enlarge, and you fall
         ECHO PLAYER in! You scream as you get flushed down the drain and into the sewer system. At
         ECHO PLAYER last you are dumped into the ocean and you wash up on the beach.
         MOVE 1941
         POSITION LAY
         AFFECT 1930
         ECHO OTHERS You hear the sound of a commode flushing... and someone screaming!
         AFFECT 1941
         ECHO OTHERS %N washes up on shore, looking quite soaked and exhausted.
      ENDIF
      IFVAR POSITION ! 1
         ECHO PLAYER The contents of the commode gurgle down the drain.
         AFFECT 1930
         ECHO OTHERS You hear the sound of a commode flushing coming from one of the stalls.
      ENDIF
   ENDIF
ENDIF

