*DESCRIPTION_START
Decorated in a sort of sea shanty motif, the display racks are draped with
fishing nets with little glass balls and seashells attached. A big brass anchor
dominates the center of the shop were it sits with trousers hanging on it. A
sign hangs on one of the walls listing the prices of the stores wares while a
skinny wooden door leads to a dressing room. You also notice a small booth in
one of the corners of the store.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 0
Perusing the racks of clothing, you find several items of interest. A sign
listing the prices of each item hangs on a nearby wall.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 1
Printed across the front of the door are the words "DRESSING ROOM".
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFPREVERB UNLATCH 1
   IFVAR INTNUM3 = 1
