      REMOVEITEM 1
      NEWITEM 1 200 ADJ1=1220 ADJ2=355 VAL2=1938 UNLATCHED
      AFFECT 1938
      REMOVEITEM 0
      NEWITEM 0 199 ADJ1=1220 ADJ2=355 VAL2=1937 UNLATCHED
