*DESCRIPTION_START
A floor-to-ceiling three sectioned jointed mirror reflects back your image upon
entering this large dressing room. Ornate brass hooks, mounted in the textured
light blue wallpaper, hang in several locations to hold your future purchases.
A well padded bench paired with its matching foot stool provides a comfortable
place to rest and contemplate your purchases. A latch on the door allows you to
privacy while you change clothes.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 0
The skinny wooden door leads back out into the Boutique. It can be latched to
allow you privacy while you change clothes.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 1
The well padded bench looks to be both functional and comfortable.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFPREVERB LEAN 1
   IFVAR POSITION = 1
      CLEARVERB
      ECHO PLAYER You lean back and place your feet up on the stool.
      ECHO OTHERS %N leans back and places %h feet up on the stool.
   ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB GO 1
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER You sit on the bench.
   ECHO OTHERS %N sits on the bench.
   POSITION SIT
ENDIF

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 2
The stool looks great for leaning back on the bench and putting your feet up.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFPREVERB LOOK 3
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER You admire your reflection.
   ECHO OTHERS %N preens in front of the mirror.
ENDIF

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 4
These brass hooks provide a place to hang your clothing while you try on your
new purchases.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFPREVERB SIT -1
   IFVAR POSITION ! 1
      CLEARVERB
      ECHO PLAYER You sit on the bench.
      ECHO OTHERS %N sits on the bench.
      POSITION SIT
   ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB LAY -1
   IFVAR POSITION ! 2
      CLEARVERB
      ECHO PLAYER You lay down in the floor.
      ECHO OTHERS %N lays down in the floor.
   ENDIF
ENDIF
