;
;
;Liberty Lane Apartments
NUMBER 1961
NAME Apartment building, Lobby
CAFE
MOVEMENT_ASTRAL
CHANNEL 777
REGION 1
INDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT

CALL 49

EXIT O 1951
EXIT N 1967

ITEM 0 350 OPEN ADJ1=535 VAL2=1951
ITEM 1 1305 ADJ1=298 ADJ2=693
EXTEND 1 that surrounds a majestic statue
ITEM 2 401 ADJ1=1123
ITEM 3 1042
ITEM 4 247 ADJ1=145
ITEM 5 362 ADJ1=239 ADJ2=150
ITEM 6 204
ITEM 7 720
ITEM 8 1594 ADJ1=292
ITEM 9 511 ADJ1=145 ADJ2=693 VAL2=1902

*DESCRIPTION_START
A plush gray rug covers most of the polished hardwood floor of this large room.
A circular couch sits in the center of the lobby, surrounding a majestic marble
statue of a familiar figure. A small sign hangs above a counter, on which rests
a silver tray. An elevator allows easy access to the floors above, a glowing
portal is recessed in one of the walls and a revolving door leads back out onto
Liberty Lane.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 0
It leads back out onto Liberty Lane.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFPREVERB CLOSE 0
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER You don't see a way to do that.
ENDIF

IFPREVERB LEAN 0
   CLEARVERB
   IFVAR POSITION ! 0
      ECHO PLAYER You'll have to stand up first.
   ELSE
      ECHO PLAYER You lean on %a.
      ECHO OTHERS %N leans on %a.
      PLREVENT 1
      CONTPLREVENT
      ECHO PLAYER The door suddenly begins to turn, and you tumble through!
      ECHO OTHERS The door suddenly begins to turn, and %N tumbles through!
      DISBAND
      MOVE 1951
      POSITION LAY
      SHOWROOM 1951
      AFFECT 1951
      ECHO OTHERS %N tumbles through a revolving door!
   ENDIF
ENDIF

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 1
The couch forms a perfect circle around a marble statue, save for a single
small opening allowing you passage to a comfortable seat.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 2
You seem to recognize who this statue is a sculpture of. Its upswept hair is
pulled into a loose twist that tries to keep the curls at bay, and the way the
light plays along the marble, it reflects an auburn shade. Its eyes, peeking
out through the escaping tendrils, seem to perkle at you.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFPREVERB EXAM 3
   CLEARVERB
   IFVAR AZAFLOORNUM ! RNUM
      ECHO PLAYER Its doors are closed. You notice a glowing button on the wall beside it.
   ELSE
      ECHO PLAYER Its doors are open.
   ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB GO 3
   CLEARVERB
   IFVAR AZAFLOORNUM ! RNUM
      ECHO PLAYER Its doors are closed. You notice a glowing button on the wall beside it.
   ELSE
      MOVEGROUP 1966
      ECHO OTHGROUP %P enters the elevator.
      AFFECT 1966
      ECHO OTHGROUP %P arrives.
   ENDIF
ENDIF

IFVERB PUSH 4
   IFVAR AZAFLOORNUM ! RNUM
      EQUAL AZAELEBUT1 1
   ELSE
      ECHO PLAYER You notice that the elevator's doors are open.
   ENDIF
ENDIF

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 5
The rug is piled very deep, your feet sinking up to your ankles. Intricately
woven threads give shape to countless tiny ice cream cones across the tapestry.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM READ 6
Welcome to the Liberty Lane apartment building. We offer one-room apartments
at the very reasonable rate of $10,000 for lifetime ownership. If you would be
interested in purcashing an apartment, please contact a host.

                     Liberty Lane Apartments directory

    Room  Occupants                     Room  Occupants
    ---------------------------------   ---------------------------------
    201 - Corey                         301 - Working
    202 - Thom & Lori                   302 - Vaughn
    203 - Haven                         303 - Foxy
    204 - Nate & Cassima                304 - UNRENTED

    Room  Occupants                     Room  Occupants
    ---------------------------------   ---------------------------------
    401 - UNRENTED                      501 - Scarlett
    402 - UNRENTED                      502 - Frances
    403 - UNRENTED                      503 - UNRENTED
    404 - UNRENTED                      504 - Ingrid
   ---------------------------------------------------------------------
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 7
On top of the counter, you see a large silver tray, much like the one found in
the Casino Central.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFVERB KICK 7
   IFVAR ROUNDTIME = 0
      EQUAL ROUNDTIME 5
      ADD FLAG1 1
      IFVAR FLAG1 = 1
         ECHO PLAYER You hear a grinding noise from behind you, as if something heavy was being
         ECHO PLAYER moved.
         ECHO OTHERS The majestic statue turns toward %N.
      ENDIF
      IFVAR FLAG1 = 2
         ECHO PLAYER Something hard hits you in the back of the head!
         ECHO OTHERS The statue reaches out and slaps %N on the back of %h noggin!
      ENDIF
      IFVAR FLAG1 = 3
         ECHO PLAYER You hear the grinding noise from behind you again.
         ECHO OTHERS The statue begins walking toward %N.
         PLREVENT 1
         CONTPLREVENT
         ECHO PLAYER You turn around and see that the statue is now directly behind you!
         ECHO OTHERS %N is shocked to see the statue standing directly behind %i.
         PLREVENT 1
         CONTPLREVENT
         ECHO PLAYER The statue lifts you over its head and throws you toward the revolving door!
         ECHO OTHERS The statue lifts %N over its head and throws %i toward the revolving door! It then slowly walks back to its original position.
         DISBAND
         MOVE 1951
         POSITION LAY
         SHOWROOM 1951
         AFFECT 1951
         ECHO OTHERS %N comes flying out the revolving door and lands on %h back!
      ENDIF
   ELSE
      STRCVT 0 ROUNDTIME
      ECHO PLAYER [Wait %0 seconds...]
   ENDIF
ENDIF

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 8
Please place your unwanted items on this tray.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 9
Directly above the glowing circular portal are the words "Jump Zone 1-B".
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFPREVERB SIT -1
   CLEARVERB
   IFVAR POSITION = 1
      ECHO PLAYER You're already sitting.
   ELSE
      ECHO PLAYER You sink deeply into the cushions of the soft couch.
      ECHO OTHERS %N sinks deeply into the cushions of the soft couch.
      POSITION SIT
   ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB LISTEN -1
   IFVAR ARCHNUM = -1
      CLEARVERB
      RANDOM DUMMY1 1 5 0
      IFVAR DUMMY1 = 1
         ECHO PLAYER The apartment building is completely silent.
      ENDIF
      IFVAR DUMMY1 = 2
         ECHO PLAYER You hear the sounds of someone vacuuming one of the floors above.
      ENDIF
      IFVAR DUMMY1 = 3
         ECHO PLAYER You hear a couple having a lovers spat from one of the rooms above.
      ENDIF
      IFVAR DUMMY1 = 4
         ECHO PLAYER You hear the groan of the elevator moving between floors.
      ENDIF
      IFVAR DUMMY1 = 5
         ECHO PLAYER The apartment building is completely silent.
      ENDIF
   ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB SMELL -1
   IFVAR ARCHNUM = -1
      CLEARVERB
      ECHO PLAYER The apartment building smells distinctly of several flavors of ice cream.
   ENDIF
ENDIF
