ITEM 1 247 ADJ1=145
EXTEND 1 labeled 1
ITEM 2 247 ADJ1=145
EXTEND 2 labeled 2
ITEM 3 247 ADJ1=145
EXTEND 3 labeled 3
ITEM 4 247 ADJ1=145
EXTEND 4 labeled 4
ITEM 5 247 ADJ1=145
EXTEND 5 labeled 5

*DESCRIPTION_START
The glowing buttons adorning a silver panel seem to be the brightest source
of light in this cramped elevator, the dimness of the room doing very little
to counter the feeling of being closed in.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFPREVERB EXAM 0
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER The panel contains five glowing buttons...%c
   ECHO PLAYER Button 1 - 1st Floor (Lobby)
   ECHO PLAYER Button 2 - 2nd Floor
   ECHO PLAYER Button 3 - 3rd Floor
   ECHO PLAYER Button 4 - 4th Floor
   ECHO PLAYER Button 5 - 5th Floor%c
   IFVAR AZAFLOORNUM = 0
      ECHO PLAYER A digital display shows that you are between floors.
   ENDIF
   IFVAR AZAFLOORNUM = 1960
      ECHO PLAYER A digital display shows that you are on the 1st floor.
   ENDIF
   IFVAR AZAFLOORNUM = 1961
      ECHO PLAYER A digital display shows that you are on the 2nd floor.
   ENDIF
   IFVAR AZAFLOORNUM = 1962
      ECHO PLAYER A digital display shows that you are on the 3rd floor.
   ENDIF
   IFVAR AZAFLOORNUM = 1963
      ECHO PLAYER A digital display shows that you are on the 4th floor.
   ENDIF
   IFVAR AZAFLOORNUM = 1964
      ECHO PLAYER A digital display shows that you are on the 5th floor.
   ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB O -1
   CLEARVERB
   IFVAR POSITION > 0
      ECHO PLAYER You'll have to stand up first.
   ELSE
      IFVAR AZAFLOORNUM ! 0
         MOVEGROUP AZAFLOORNUM
         ECHO OTHGROUP %P goes out.
         AFFECT AZAFLOORNUM
         ECHO OTHGROUP %P arrives from the elevator.
      ELSE
         ECHO PLAYER The elevator doors are closed.
      ENDIF
   ENDIF
ENDIF

