;
;TEST APARTMENT
NUMBER 1967
NAME Apartment (Demonstration Model)
CAFE
MOVEMENT_ASTRAL
CHANNEL 777
REGION 1
INDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT

CALL 49

RELOGIN 1961
EXIT O 1961

ITEM 0 475 ADJ1=966
ITEM 1 1304 ADJ1=298 ADJ2=180
ITEM 2 91 ADJ1=480
ITEM 3 91 ADJ1=1170
ITEM 4 85 ADJ1=1145 ADJ2=32
ITEM 5 195 ADJ1=33
PUT 5 196 ADJ1=196
ITEM 6 381 ADJ1=216
ITEM 7 192 ADJ1=291
ITEM 8 193 ADJ1=367

*DESCRIPTION_START
This room has been set-up to aid you in designing your own apartment. In the
center of the room is a soft leather sofa with an end table at one end and a
long coffee table placed in front of it. On one wall, a picture window looks
out on Liberty Lane, while across the room a brick fireplace, containing some
fake logs, adds to the atmosphere. In a far corner of the room is a king-size
brass bed draped with silk sheets and piled high with fluffy pillows.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 0
Looking through the window, you see the front of the apartment building and
the wooden bridge the crosses over the pond in the center of Liberty Lane.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 1
The soft leather sofa looks very comfortable.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 2
It's just your normal every-day coffee table.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 3
It's just your normal every-day end table.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 4
The king-size brass bed, draped with silk sheets and piled high with fluffy
pillows, looks very comfortable and large enough to hold several people. But
being just a demonstration model, you don't feel like testing that theory.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFPREVERB GO 4
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER The bed is just a demonstration model. It wasn't meant to be actually used.
ENDIF

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 5
The brick fireplace has been filled with fake plastic logs burning with fake
plastic flames. Above it is an oak mantle lined with picture frames that hold
pictures of anonymous "model" families.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 6
The rich oak mantle has been stained a dark brown and polished to a bright
shining glow.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 7
The silk sheets are draped across the bed in a lazy yet elegant way. Cool to
the touch, they make you want to climb into bed for a quick nap.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 8
The fluffy pillow looks like it would heavenly to rest your head upon.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFPREVERB LAY -1
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER There's no place to lay here.
ENDIF

IFPREVERB SIT -1
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER You take a seat and relax on the comfortable sofa.
   ECHO OTHERS %N takes a seat and relaxes on the comfortable sofa.
ENDIF
